column2: "If you're not in any particular hurry, I recommend not proceeding any farther."
"Any farther than this will put you in danger..."
"As you can see, Master Gettemhart is treating everything he sees as an enemy right now."
"You're correct, there's no distinguishing this from senseless violence."
"If you proceed, you might get caught up in it. Even I would not be safe."
"You may think that the way he treats me is cruel, but that is only how it appears from your perspective."
"As long as I can be with him, I have more than enough."
"I do not allow myself to want any more. Above all else, that is the one thing I cannot allow."
"It seems our conversation must end here."
